title: Macintosh 68K Emulation Pack
description:
Macintosh 68K Emulation Pack

This is a Basilisk II compatible hard disk image with Mac OS 7.6.1 with about 100 apps and 380 classic mac games. The HD image expands up to almost 2 gigabytes!

Install instructions and a version of Basilisk II for Windows users are included. 

I didn't create this image. I lost my first copy - thanks to a forum member whose name starts with T for making it available again! Hopefully hosting here will keep it available for anyone who wants it going forward.


Have fun with this great classic software collection!
